'''西南财大站'''位于[[中国|中国]][[四川省|四川省]][[成都市|成都市]][[青羊区|青羊区]]清江中路二环路口，是[[成都地铁4号线|成都地铁4号线]]的地下岛式车站，于2015年12月26日启用<ref name="启用">{{cite news | title = 成都地铁4号线一期工程载客运营 首列车为“青创号”(组图) | publisher = 网易 | date = 2015-12-26 | url = http://news.163.com/15/1226/09/BBOHURKI00014AED.html | accessdate = 2015-12-26 | language = zh | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171210124220/http://news.163.com/15/1226/09/BBOHURKI00014AED.html | archive-date = 2017-12-10 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。临近[[西南财经大学|西南财大]]光华校区而得名<ref>{{cite news | title = 咱校门口有4个地铁站｜地铁时代，请收下这份西财人专属出行指南 | publisher = 搜狐 | date = 2017-06-08 | url = http://www.sohu.com/a/147222590_407282 | accessdate = 2017-06-08 | language = zh | archive-date = 2019-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191129000052/http://www.sohu.com/a/147222590_407282 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。临近[[峨眉电影集团|峨眉电影集团]]，站台装饰以电影为主题<ref>{{cite news | title = 这居然是成都牛逼地铁站！你到过几个？！ | publisher = 乐居 | date = 2016-09-19 | url = http://sc.leju.com/scan/2016-09-19/07106183178175552741313.shtml | accessdate = 2016-09-19 | language = zh | archive-date = 2019-12-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191215192355/https://sc.leju.com/scan/2016-09-19/07106183178175552741313.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。因紧邻成温立交，本站在建设过程中的工程名为“成温立交站”<ref>{{cite news  | title = 成都4号线等三条地铁线路同时开工  | publisher = 新浪  | date = 2011-12-28  | url = http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2011-12-28/145123710124.shtml  | accessdate = 2011-12-28  | language = zh  | archive-date = 2017-08-14  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170814134552/http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2011-12-28/145123710124.shtml  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>。
